      <title>新手CentOS6 配置 静态ip地址</title>
      <link href="2021/01/20/xin-shou-centos6-an-zhuang-jing-tai-ip-di-zhi/"/>
      <url>2021/01/20/xin-shou-centos6-an-zhuang-jing-tai-ip-di-zhi/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p><font color=#999AAA >以CentOS6 VMware 15.5.0为基础</font></p><hr style=" border:solid; width:100px; height:1px;" color=#000000 size=1"><h1 id="一、CentOS6的安装（略）"><a href="#一、CentOS6的安装（略）" class="headerlink" title="一、CentOS6的安装（略）"></a>一、CentOS6的安装（略）</h1><p>可以参考此文章 <a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/dca2d94dc1ab">简书-Y先生的领地CentOS6.5系统安装</a><br>或者自行百度CentOS6的安装</p><h1 id="二、设置静态ip地址"><a href="#二、设置静态ip地址" class="headerlink" title="二、设置静态ip地址"></a>二、设置静态ip地址</h1><h2 id="1-物理机和vm的设置"><a href="#1-物理机和vm的设置" class="headerlink" title="1.物理机和vm的设置"></a>1.物理机和vm的设置</h2><p><strong>1.1</strong> vm客户端的编辑：</p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2021/01/20/uJiwnkEjK3M8HfV.jpg"></p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201024124508775.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3drOTM0NTMw,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201024124855655.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3drOTM0NTMw,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br><strong>1.12</strong> 物理机网络配置：<br>打开控制面板 》网络和Internet 》网络连接<br><strong>注：虚拟机的ip地址下面地址要同一个网段</strong><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201024132432665.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3drOTM0NTMw,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><h2 id="2-centos6配置ip地址"><a href="#2-centos6配置ip地址" class="headerlink" title="2.centos6配置ip地址"></a>2.centos6配置ip地址</h2><p><strong>2.1 <font color=#999AAA >代码如下：</strong></p><pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">vim <span class="token operator">/</span>etc<span class="token operator">/</span>sysconfig<span class="token operator">/</span>network<span class="token operator">-</span>scripts<span class="token operator">/</span>ifcfg<span class="token operator">-</span>eth0</code></pre><pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">静态网络设定：DEVICE=eth0ONBOOT=no    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#修改为yes</span>IPADDR=192<span class="token punctuation">.</span>168<span class="token punctuation">.</span>xx<span class="token punctuation">.</span>xx    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#增加这一行,与上面地址为同一个网段，最后以为尽量大于129</span>NETMASK=255<span class="token punctuation">.</span>255<span class="token punctuation">.</span>255<span class="token punctuation">.</span>0BOOTPROTO=none    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#修改为static</span>GATEWAY=192<span class="token punctuation">.</span>168<span class="token punctuation">.</span>XX<span class="token punctuation">.</span>XX    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#NAT设置里面的网关ip一致</span></code></pre><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201024134949376.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3drOTM0NTMw,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p><p>  注：按i进入编辑，wq保存<br><strong>2.2 保存退出后执行以下命令，网卡重启</strong></p><pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">service network restert</code></pre><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201024140138945.png#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br><strong>2.3查看ip地址是否修改成功</strong></p><pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">ifconfig</code></pre><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201024140947344.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3drOTM0NTMw,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>注：若int addr（圈红地方）地址还是为127.0.0.1   应该重启网卡就能解决<br><strong>2.4 修改 主机名与ip地址的映射关系</strong></p><pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">vim <span class="token operator">/</span>etc<span class="token operator">/</span>hosts</code></pre><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201024142625465.png#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>注：按i键进行修改，wq保存并退出</p><p><strong>2.5 重启centos6</strong></p><pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">reboot</code></pre><p>注：重启系统，主机名才会生效</p><p><strong>2.6验证物理机和centos6是否互通</strong></p><pre class=" language-powershell"><code class="language-powershell">ping 192<span class="token punctuation">.</span>168<span class="token punctuation">.</span>xx<span class="token punctuation">.</span>xx <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#此地址为物理机网络配置地址</span></code></pre><p>此说明 centos6能通物理机<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201024143808406.png#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br>此说明 物理机能centos6<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201024144245192.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3drOTM0NTMw,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br> end</p><hr style=" border:solid; width:100px; height:1px;" color=#000000 size=1"><p><font color=#999AAA >大神勿喷，若安装代码，请指正：<br>正在学习Linux操作系统的小白。如果你也是刚学习Linux的话，可以交流交流。</p>]]></content>
      
      
